Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:06.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was helping some upperclassmen from the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Banri, what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:12.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so close with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same club, and we have a lot in common...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl Yana likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:29.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not right for you to be so close with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're acting a little weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weird one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:40.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I think Kaga-san would feel bad if she saw you two just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:43.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:57.01,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(299,299)}His Chasm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:01:06.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:31.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:39.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:43.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:55.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:03.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:07.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:16.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So Linda-senpai is uncomfortable with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had sort of suspected it from the way she was acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But what really surprised me was Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't seem like herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Miss Ultrasonic has a lot of feelings on the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she said all that because she does,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but wasn't that a little one-sided of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:58.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know that you and\NLinda-senpai were classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:02.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's my fault that I haven't told her yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:03.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked you were being so friendly with Linda-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,that Miss Ultrasonic got upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was her mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:17.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were just having a frank conversation as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't doing anything inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:29.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been able to put a lot behind me since going to the reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was fine when I heard that Yana-san likes Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:38.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I want to support him from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like just a normal friend, praying for my friends to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The person most important to me right now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the right time to give her the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'd follow naturally from this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The location is beautiful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I always screw up at times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget something on campus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going back, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... no... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Yana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Stuck with senpai girls. Can't get away.\NRequesting immediate rescue."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:47.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I also bailed on him, saying I was going to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When is the best time to give it to her, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly wait until Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:22.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could ask Oka-chan for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who else I could talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:56.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:01.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual that we end up on the same train in the morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So even you go to college in the morning sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to miss much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not get enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like a good time to ask her about the ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:34.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's not with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kouko has a first period class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She visited your apartment while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when she did the exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:54.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the "exorcist"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't tell you, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:02.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But... I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kouko rotate her head 180 degrees or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So Yana-san really started filming the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's apparently going to keep coming until the school festival next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if he can't get closer to Linda-senpai before then, he fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But the festival club doesn't even practice every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mitsuo's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys got here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you skip class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Our lectures just ended early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaga-san, let's go to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:53.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Their limited-time Belgian chocolate soft serve is on sale now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:08:00.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The Belgian chocolate I've been waiting since last year to see on sale again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have class this afternoon, and I've got work after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:07.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Without Belgian chocolate,\NI just don't feel like working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:10.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't work, I won't be able to pay my taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fail as a cog in the machine of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better go, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do my part, so you can do your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you call {\i1}noblesse oblige!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, I'm going to go eat Belgian chocolate with Miss Ultrasonic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,to secure our nation's financial resources!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're done with classes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you somewhere.\NCall me when you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They've really grown close, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good comes of those two getting together, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They left the three of us to go have fun on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:53.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan didn't even look at me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's it going, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are your visits to the festival club paying off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you still haven't had a real conversation with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've talked a little bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked if she wanted to see what I'd filmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,she said, "No, that's okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:23.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's still mad at me for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We've grown farther apart than we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She left so quickly yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This so hopeless, I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die over that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You and Kaga-san aren't doing enough, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're always there with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:46.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're not helping your friend enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But Yana-san's free to come and go as he pleases at the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! The festival club's defenses are pretty tough to breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They don't have any defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:03.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, those second year girls are kicking down all defenses themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:06.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I mean their defenses around Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, the president, Koshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosshi-senpai's a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell he's a really nice guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:20.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but he's always watching Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I try to approach her, he casually leads her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's obviously trying to protect Linda-senpai from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:28.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:32.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Class is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you're right! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. My class ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have practice with the festival club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:03.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about where we could go and what we could do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So? Where should we go, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the "exorcist"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-senpai mentioned it this morning on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-wh-who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely, totally no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:38.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But Nana-senpai said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to go see another one of Nana-senpai's concerts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with Linda-senpai, Mitsuo,\NMiss Ultrasonic, and 2D-kun next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:54.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be busy with the Awa dance and school festival for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But once those are over, let's have lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to all kinds of places and see all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:11.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope our days stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to give her that ring soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that I'm just thinking about this too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:39.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should just casually give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sao-chan from the tea club!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:53.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everything going well with your beautiful girlfriend? You rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, very well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,D-don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving it to your girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're proposing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When a man gives a girl a ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,it means he wants her to marry him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, giving a ring equals a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But what's with this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even wrapped. It's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out her size?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't want the ring to be too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really not that big of a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom wore this ring when she was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to give it to my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...wore that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...when she was younger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the overreaction for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too meaningful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:58.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:04.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It totally means she wants you to bring her home and show off the ring on her finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:05.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:09.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think my mom put that much thought into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're too immature, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should join the tea club and cultivate your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing that up again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:26.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see, all the boys we dragged into the club in April ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently recruiting male club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come check us out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:35.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've got festival club practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, Shi-chan, we're going to be late ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri, you should hang out with us sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:48.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like they just raised the bar as high as it'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. My lecture ran late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't keep everyone waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's been decided
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:08.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,that the fourth years will be participating in this Sunday's festival on short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today's our last day to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you all work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The former president still hasn't found a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:24.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to take another break for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:26.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's start with some stretches!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Linda-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda! Help the fourth years with their dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember how to put on your costumes, and the choreography?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were away for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't danced at all since becoming a fourth year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Mitsuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder if Hosshi-san and the other fourth years will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They only had today to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:09.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little worried about them, but festivals are a place to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If this'll cheer Hosshi-san up, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:21.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, have you talked to Oka-chan since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I try to talk about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,she says she has something to do and runs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:34.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It might be best to leave her alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's focus on the festival for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about everything else later, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:49.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you think about what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:05.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people will be coming, so you should secure a spot to film early.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be difficult to film from the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move off a bit and wait where the crowd starts to thin out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of people here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're all really pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to look bad or embarrass themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:30.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll abandon my personal feelings and focus on filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, I'll be filming you, so make sure you look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:33.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go find a spot to film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've got far more experience than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:51.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's been so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... how do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For that... Kosshi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko doesn't seem to be too nervous today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's so focused on taking care of the fourth years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:08.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,she can't afford to be nervous herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.59,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(437,50)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Golden
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.59,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(482,89)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.59,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(282,272)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Golden
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:11.59,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(322,310)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time for us to show the results of our practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:31.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, festival club!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The world's shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's bathed in a golden light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second ago, I was waiting for Linda on the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:00.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was waiting for Linda on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I suddenly thrown into this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko-chan's looking for you somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was just dancing with Kouko until a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:12.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But... why did my memories up to the day after graduation suddenly come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:16.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, seriously, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go back to Kouko and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:26.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my memories suddenly return?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to take over my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:50.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...my existence again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chigau yo mou, chigau tteba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa, mada kizukanai no ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ni san jikan mo mae kara sono ude ni furetai noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:28.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:38.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sakebitai kimochi wa hora komaru hodo aru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite doushite chittomo aa satotte kurenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:51.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne hontou ni hontou ni watashi ni koi shiteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosabayui kotoba wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Han eikyuuteki ni ai shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gosen-nen go nado kyoumi wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi endless de wa nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:10.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuka wa shinu no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:17.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Eien ni ai shiteru yo" nante yuwaretemo ureshikunai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mazu wa watashi o shinu made
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ai suru koto dake o kangaete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:40.98,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(55,410)}I'll Be Back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:30.27,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(189,366)}How dare you act so happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:32.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(170,366)}You're so impudent, Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.51,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(191,366)}Happiness won't come to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.51,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(140,366)}That's why we go out searching for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:39.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(235,366)}Come on, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.58,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(326,363)}Yeah!
